                     <interp inst="t18520816-804-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 watch, value 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and 5 shillings; the property of <persName id="t18520816-name-186" type="victimName">
