                        <interp inst="t18520816-name-188" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SHAW</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City-policeman</hi>, 224). I took the prisoner to the station, I found on him these five shillings—this watch was in the leg of his trowsers, fastened to the bottom of the trowsers by this chain.</p>
